RXR 1
NAME appkit-sampler
APP appkit_sampler.rxe
FILE appkit_sampler.rxe
RXE 1
ID app-appkit-sampler
NAME APPKIT Sampler
ICON A
LAYOUT panel
COLOR 0xFF6CC0A8
INPUT Value:
BUTTON Build
USE APPKIT
UI PANEL 0 0 250 36 APPKIT Sampler
UI BUTTON 8 8 78 20 Build | 4
UI TOGGLE 0 46 118 22 Toggle | on
UI SLIDER 130 46 140 18 Slider | 62
UI PROGRESS 0 76 220 18 Progress | 44
UI CUSTOM knob 230 76 92 24 Custom | twist
UI OUTPUT 0 112 0 0 Sampler output
DESKTOP 1
DOCK 0
TEXT Demonstrates several APPKIT widgets from an RXR bundle.
LANG C
CODE appkit("UI BADGE 330 9 80 18 runtime");
CODE println(input + 44);
CODE lsh("type appkit_sampler_notes.lardd");
ENDFILE
FILE appkit_sampler_notes.lardd
LARDD 1
TITLE APPKIT Sampler Notes
TEXT This RXR bundle demonstrates file-defined widgets and runtime appkit output.
TEXT It is meant for app authors on the app branch.
END
ENDFILE
END
